---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Contact information for Betting Maths."
>
  <section class="content-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact Betting Maths</p>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Betting Maths is currently a simple educational website and does not offer a direct contact email address or contact form.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Please note:</strong> Betting Maths cannot provide betting tips, predictions, personalised gambling advice or support with gambling losses.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>No direct contact details at the moment</h2>
    <p>
      At the moment, Betting Maths does not provide a public email address, contact form or customer support service.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is currently focused on offering free calculators and plain-English betting maths guides. A contact option may be added in future if the site expands.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>About the site</h2>
    <p>
      Betting Maths is designed to explain betting concepts such as odds, implied probability, overround, dutching, hedging, bookmaker margin, back bets, lay bets and liability.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is for educational purposes only and is not a personalised advice service.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Need help with gambling?</h2>
    <p>
      If you are looking for gambling support rather than calculator information, please visit the <a href="/responsible-gambling/">Responsible Gambling</a> page.
    </p>
    <p>
      That page includes support resources and safer gambling information.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      <strong>Important:</strong> If gambling is causing stress, debt or harm, it is better to seek help from a dedicated support service rather than rely on gambling websites or calculators.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card article-section">
    <h2>Future updates</h2>
    <p>
      If Betting Maths adds a public email address, contact form or other feedback option in future, this page will be updated.
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .article-section {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .article-section a {
      color: var(--color-green-dark);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
